  "introduced_at": "1995-01-11", 
  "number": "491", 
  "official_title": "To amend titles II and XVIII of the Social Security Act to ensure the integrity of the social security trust funds by reconstituting the Boards of Trustees of such trust funds and the Managing Trustee of such trust funds to increase their independence, by providing for annual investment plans to guide investment of amounts in such trust funds, and by removing unnecessary restrictions on investment and disinvestment of amounts in such trust funds.", 
